data.description: This meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath, concrete block home is located in the highly sought after neighborhood of Grande Champion in the LPGA community. The large office can be very easily converted into a 4th bedroom.  The master bath is an absolute must-see with the huge stand-up shower, and jetted tub. Don't forget the massive walk-in closet with custom shelving! Freshly painted inside and out (including the garage). 9 foot ceilings throughout. Granite counter tops.  42 inch kitchen cabinets with custom wine rack. Double pane windows. New carpet. New tile in guest bathroom. Tropical landscaping. The entire home is also HANDICAP ACCESSIBLE! Community pool. Close to I4 & I95, Tanger Outlets, schools, hospitals, and yes.... THE BEACH!!
